            <h1 class='main-title animated zoomIn mb-4'>Brainstorming: o que é e quais suas regras?</h1>
            <div class='d-flex mb-2 detail-post'>
              <small><i class='far fa-user me-2'></i><a href='./blog?authorID=28'>Lucas</a> | <a href='./blog?categoryID=13'>Gerais</a></small>
